snippet.title: Dustoff Z Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Get those blades spinning, Dustoff Z will takeoff in fall 2020 on Nintendo Switch, PS4, Xbox One & PC!
Wishlist today on Steam: https://bit.ly/DustoffZ 

The time has come to rebuild humanity! Dustoff Z is a game about maneuvering combat-helicopters in one of the harshest weather conditions possible – A Zombie Apocalypse.
